Name: XPB2800 (SPB2800MC) Wedge Belt Continental CONTITECH
Short Description:
Brand:Continental CONTITECH
Belt Section:  XPB
Datum Length:  2800mm
Top Width:  16mm
Depth:  13mm
Belt Construction:  Moulded Cog
Description:
XPB2800 (SPB2800MC) Wedge Belt Continental CONTITECH
Moulded Cog or Raw-edge V-belts have higher capacity and efficiency and they use smaller pulleys than traditional envelope (wrapped) belts. These belts have a higher coefficient of friction and are more aggressive, which makes them a very efficient belt for power transmission Unlike conventional fabric-covered V-belts, raw-edge belts have no cover. Thus, the cross-sectional area normally occupied by the cover is used for more load-carrying cord. Cogs on the inner surface of the belt increase air flow to enhance cooler running. They also increase flexibility, allowing the belt to operate with smaller pulleys.
